{"fadein":1.5,"once":true,"id":"DEYIZHI6","fadeType":2,"mode":2,"fadeOut":1.5,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"sequence":[["The Cloudy Mask\n\n<size=45>Chapter 6: The Truth, Pt. 2<\/size>",1]],"stopbgm":true},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"flashout":{"black":true,"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1]},"hideOther":true,"flashin":{"black":true,"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0]},"side":0,"subActors":[{"pos":{"x":1500},"actor":403040}],"bgm":"story-1","nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"It's all because of that name... \"Lützow.\"","dir":1,"bgmDelay":2,"actor":405020},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"hideOther":true,"side":0,"subActors":[{"pos":{"x":1500},"actor":403040}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"say":"Indeed. I don't know how it came to be, but she isn't just Deutschland of the Iron Blood, she was also born as Lützow of the Northern Parliament.","actor":404020},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"action":[{"number":2,"x":0,"type":"shake","delay":0,"dur":0.2,"y":45}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Huh?! How do they know that...?!","actor":403040},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"hideOther":true,"side":0,"subActors":[{"pos":{"x":1500},"actor":403040}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"say":"And not the Lützow who fought in the Great War, the one the Northern Parliament refloated...","actor":404020},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"hideOther":true,"side":0,"subActors":[{"pos":{"x":1500},"actor":403040}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"say":"Her history haunts her. So she tried desperately to make herself out as the ideal image of Iron Blood so we'd accept her.","actor":403030},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"... Why would she bring this up now...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":403040},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"hideOther":true,"side":0,"subActors":[{"pos":{"x":1500},"actor":403040}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"say":"Sure, she had a thing with the Northern Parliament, but she's still Deutschland. She's one of us.","actor":401010},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"hideOther":true,"side":0,"subActors":[{"pos":{"x":1500},"actor":403040}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"say":"And we wanted to make her feel like a part of the team, but since she's kinda sensitive, we agreed to be nice to her.","actor":401010},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"......……","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":403040},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"So basically, they were simply doing their best not to hurt or upset her.","dir":1},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"hideOther":true,"side":0,"subActors":[{"pos":{"x":1500},"actor":403040}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"say":"Which is why we kept this a secret from her and accepted her into the Iron Blood.","actor":404020},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"hideOther":true,"side":0,"subActors":[{"pos":{"x":1500},"actor":403040}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"say":"That's right. Above all else, she is one of us. But ironically, all our cautiousness and special treatment wound up hurting her in the end...","actor":405020},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"hideOther":true,"side":0,"subActors":[{"pos":{"x":1500},"actor":403040}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"say":"I think she's fine the way she is right now... but I guess she should come to terms with herself, at least a little.","actor":401010},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"hideOther":true,"side":0,"subActors":[{"pos":{"x":1500},"actor":403040}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"say":"It might leave her feeling blue for a while, but maybe we should tell her the truth?","actor":401010},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"hideOther":true,"side":0,"subActors":[{"pos":{"x":1500},"actor":403040}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"say":"I say we do. It's a shame to lose the arrogant Deutschland we know, but it's time she accepts herself for who she is.","actor":403030},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"So... they pretty much admit they lied to me...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":403040},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Deutschland whispers while her shoulders tremble. Her voice lacks its signature impactful tone, instead sounding frail.","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"... Slave, let me go.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":403040},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"black":true,"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0]},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"nameColor":"#a9f548","flashout":{"black":true,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1]},"dir":1,"say":"In conclusion, we should tell Deutschland the truth.","actor":404020},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":1,"say":"But how do we go about telling her that...","paintingFadeOut":{"time":0.5,"side":0},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","actor":403050},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"We don't need to do anything. Right, Gneisenau?","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":403030},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"I let go of Deutschland. She walks over to open the door, then steps into the salon.","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"... Ah, so you knew she was listening, Eugen.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":404020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Heheh, of course I knew. So, what do you plan to do with us, Deutschland?","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":403030},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"After a brief silence, the girl raises her voice and speaks her mind.","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"You will pay dearly for deceiving me for so long.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":403040},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"But... I also want to say...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":403040},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Thank you... for accepting me.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":403040}]}